guess
=====
- filepath     Text
- type         MediaType
- title        Text
- year         Number    (only for movies)
- releasegroup Text
- source       Text
- season       Number    (only for episodes)
- episode      Number    (only for episodes)

identificator
=============
- type: MediaType
- tmdb:    Text
- tvdb:    Text   (only for episodes)
- imdb:    Text
- episode: Number (only for episodes)
- season:  Number (only for episodes)

actor
=====
- name: Text
- role: Text

movie-metadata
==============
- title: Text
- originaltitle: Text
- premiered: Date
- tagline: Text
- plot: Text
- set: Text
- certification: Text
- rating: Number
- votes: Number
- studios: List<Text>
- countries: List<Text>
- genres: List<Text>
- directors: List<Text>
- scriptwriters: List<Text>
- actors: List<actor>

tvshow-metadata
===============
- title: Text
- premiered: Date
- plot: Text
- certification: Text
- rating: Number
- votes: Number
- studios: List<Text>
- genres: List<Text>
- actors: List<actor>

episode-metadata
================
- title: Text
- showtitle: Text
- plot: Text
- premiered: Date
- rating: Number
- votes: Number

flow
guess provider -> identificator provider -> metadata provider -> write from template
                                         -> image provider    -> download
                                         -> video provider    -> youtube-dl

guess providers
===============
get_guess:
	input:  filepath, config
	output: guess

identificator providers
=======================
get_identificator_list:
	output: list<Text>
	note: imdb, tvdb... etc
get_identificator:
	input:  guess, identificator, config
	output: identificator

metadata providers:
===================
get_movie_metadata:
	input:  identifictor, metadatatype, language, config
	output: movie_metadata
get_episode_metadata:
	input:  identifictor, metadatatype, language, config
	output: episode_metadata
get_tvshow_metadata:
	input:  identifictor, metadatatype, language, config
	output: episode_metadata

image providers:
================
get_movie_image
	input: identificator, imagetype, language, config
	output: url
get_tvshow_image
	input: identificator, imagetype, language, config
	output: url
get_season_image
	input: identificator, imagetype, language, config
	output: url
get_episode_image
	input: identificator, imagetype, language, config
	output: url

Note:
The config is always the provider specific config
Every provider should have a init, which checks config
and tells programm what they are able to do


ImageTypes
==========
movie:
	- poster
	- background
	- disc
	- banner
	- logo
	- clearart
	- art
tvshow:
	- poster
	- background
	- banner
	- logo
	- clearart
	- charart
	- art
season:
	- poster
episode:
	- thumbnail
